{"tid":1171314,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"南韓女團AOA成員智珉臉頰凹陷瘦得不成人形　近照曝光令粉絲擔憂","createTime":"2019-05-25T15:21:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-25T15:28:59.000Z","uid":9573,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"64c0a637817418d1000756f493383f8cff6eadb4","tid":1171314,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T15:21:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.nownews.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/1558610109-23206b05645026b987bb38192b4fc993-696x464.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nownews.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F05%2F1558610109-23206b05645026b987bb38192b4fc993-696x464.jpg&h=c558f424&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲智珉暴瘦。<br />\n<br />\n南韓女團AOA成員智珉長相甜美，深受粉絲歡迎，原本身材玲瓏有致的她，2月被發現她瘦成皮包骨，當時公司否認她罹患厭食症，並強調她非常健康，20日智珉PO出近照，瘦得像竹竿一樣的腿，讓粉絲擔心不已。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.nownews.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/1558610052-06c38ee94d757031c23b5633b933de52.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nownews.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F05%2F1558610052-06c38ee94d757031c23b5633b933de52.jpg&h=9e4eb93f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲智珉臉蛋變超尖。<br />\n <br />\n智珉最新PO出貼文中，她身穿牛仔褲與露肚上衣，開心對著鏡頭大笑，只見她下巴非常尖，鎖骨也顯而易見，腰圍更是小的誇張。20日她PO出坐在街頭吃冰淇淋的照片，她穿著藍色寬鬆上衣，下半身搭配緊身內搭褲，雙腿明顯纖細，大腿更是不成比例，瘦得相當驚人。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.nownews.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/1558610020-2fc2d43faac8efe19380c22e09fab78f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nownews.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F05%2F1558610020-2fc2d43faac8efe19380c22e09fab78f.jpg&h=01312d79&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲智珉瘦得不成人形。<br />\n<br />\n照片曝光後，讓粉絲相當擔心智珉的健康狀況，紛紛回覆「拜託請多吃一點！」、「真的看起來非常像厭食症患者啊，越來越乾瘦了」、「瘦得有點恐怖」。雖然公司澄清智珉健康狀況良好，但與過往擁有完美比例身材的她，模樣仍差了許多。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img-s-msn-com.akamaized.net/tenant/amp/entityid/BBRHwja.img?h=416&amp;w=799&amp;m=6&amp;q=60&amp;u=t&amp;o=f&amp;l=f&amp;x=1684&amp;y=1618\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg-s-msn-com.akamaized.net%2Ftenant%2Famp%2Fentityid%2FBBRHwja.img%3Fh%3D416%26w%3D799%26m%3D6%26q%3D60%26u%3Dt%26o%3Df%26l%3Df%26x%3D1684%26y%3D1618&h=f85ccd52&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲智珉以前身材比例正常。"},{"pid":"8bd5f6c2e0ac611334da960bf6a9c7210860b8cd","tid":1171314,"uid":152432,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T15:28:59.000Z","msg":"善心打破0回覆"}]}